Package: ConfusionTableR
Type: Package
Title: Creates varied sized data frames for trained caret models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gary Hutson
Maintainer: Gary Hutson <gary.hutson.uk@hotmail.co.uk>
Description: Takes the outputs of a caret confusion matrix and allows for the quick converion of these list items to data frames.
    This extends the functionality of the powerful CARET confusion matrix functions
